  Assizecourt Amos of Team Rivers (Green) wrestles with John Emmanuel of Team Ondo State (white), during a semi-final 74kg wrestling match at the 19th National Sports Festival in Abuja in Abuja on Saturday (15/12/18). John Emmanuel won the match. NAN  Aduo Erekpo of Team Edo (Red) wrestles with John Emmanuel of Team Ondo State (white), during a group stage 74kg wrestling match at the 19th National Sports Festival in Abuja in Abuja on Saturday (15/12/18). John Emmanuel won the match, proceeds to the final. NAN